'''PyMC3'''是一个[[Python|Python]]包，用于[[贝叶斯统计|贝叶斯统计]]建模和概率机器学习，它聚焦于高级马尔可夫链蒙特卡洛法和变分拟合算法<ref>
Salvatier J, Wiecki TV, Fonnesbeck C. (2016) Probabilistic programming in Python using PyMC3. PeerJ Computer Science 2:e55 https://doi.org/10.7717/peerj-cs.55</ref><ref name="Martin2016">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=t6PcDgAAQBAJ&dq=%22PyMC3%22|title=Bayesian Analysis with Python|last1=Martin|first1=Osvaldo|date=2016|publisher=Packt Publishing Ltd|isbn=9781785889851|pages=31–60|language=en|access-date=16 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rMKiCgAAQBAJ|title=Bayesian Methods for Hackers: Probabilistic Programming and Bayesian Inference|last=Davidson-Pilon|first=Cameron|date=2015-09-30|publisher=Addison-Wesley Professional|isbn=9780133902921|language=en}}
</ref>。它是从以前版本的PyMC软件从头开始写成的<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://docs.pymc.io/intro.html|title=Introduction — PyMC3 3.1 documentation|website=docs.pymc.io|language=en|access-date=2017-09-20|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118101044/https://docs.pymc.io/intro.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==概述==
不同于使用[[Fortran|Fortran]]扩展进行计算的PyMC2，PyMC3依靠[[Theano|Theano]]来[[自动微分|自动微分]]，还有计算优化和动态[[C语言|C]]编译<ref name="Martin2016" /><ref>
{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=E93SBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA342&dq=PyMC3|title=Python for Finance: Analyze Big Financial Data|last=Hilpisch|first=Yves|date=2014-12-11|publisher=O'Reilly Media, Inc.|isbn=9781491945391|language=en}}
</ref>。从版本3.8开始PyMC3依据{{en-link|ArviZ}}来处理绘图、分析和统计检查。PyMC3和{{en-link|Stan (软件)|Stan (software)|Stan}}是两个最流行的[[概率编程|概率编程]]工具<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.fastforwardlabs.com/2017/01/30/the-algorithms-behind-probabilistic-programming.html|title=The Algorithms Behind Probabilistic Programming|access-date=2017-03-10|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129014013/https://blog.fastforwardlabs.com/2017/01/30/the-algorithms-behind-probabilistic-programming.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

PyMC3是[[开源软件|开源]]项目，由社区开发并在财务上得到NumFocus赞助<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.numfocus.org/blog/numfocus-announces-new-fiscally-sponsored-project-pymc3|title=NumFOCUS Announces New Fiscally Sponsored Project: PyMC3|work=NumFOCUS {{!}} Open Code = Better Science|access-date=2017-03-10|archive-date=2017-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921144216/https://www.numfocus.org/blog/numfocus-announces-new-fiscally-sponsored-project-pymc3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。PyMC3已经在很多领域中被用于解决推断问题，包括[[天文学|天文学]]<ref>
